<h>for loop </h>
 
Syntax:
   for i in range( start , end [, step]               // i dosen't take end. i.e. it stops at end-1 ; By default step is => i=i+1
        step 1. inside 'for loop'                     // Statements inside 'for loop' should be indented
                ...
        step last. inside 'for loop'
        
        
 
<h> while loop</h>

Syntax :
 i = start
 while( i < end )
    step 1. inside 'for loop'                     // Statements inside 'while loop' should be indented
                ...
    step n. inside 'for loop'
    
    step last. step                               //step means update condition
